Encapsulation in Java (Simple Example)

Encapsulation = Hiding data using private variables and accessing them using getter and setter methods.



class func {

    String name;

    public String getname() {
        return name;
    }

    public void setname(String nam) {
        name = nam;
    }
}

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {

        func s = new func();

        s.setname("jayasri");

        System.out.println(s.getname());
    }
}



